Package seng202.team4.model

Class Airline

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.team4.model.DataType
      • seng202.team4.model.Airline
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validate
    public class Airline
extends DataType
    Airline model class with attributes representing the aspects of airlines. These attributes were chosen from the open flights sample data. Objects of this class are created to display in the table on the Airline tab.
